<view class="programme-header">
  <view class="programme-header-title">7日减脂方案</view>
  <view class="title-box">
      <image src="../../images/caseDetails/red.png" ></image>
      <view class="box-text">帮你少摄入了约 90%糖类</view>
      <image src="../../images/caseDetails/blue.png" ></image>
      <view class="box-text-right">少摄入的热量相当于 跑了52公里 </view>
  </view>
</view>
  <view class="programme-body">
    <view class="day-list-content">
      <view class="day-list">
          <view class="{{radiusHeader}}" style="background:#FFFFFF;"  wx:key='{{index}}'>
            <view class="day-list-title" data-index='{{index + 1}}' catchtap="ifShow" >
                <view class="executeorder">DAY1</view>
                <view class="day-title">断糖启动日</view>
                <image  src="../../images/caseDetails/{{showIndex == index + 1 ? 'bottom':'top'}}.png"></image>
            </view>
            <view class="day-subtitle">减脂第一天，先来清清身体里的“糖"吧!</view>
          </view>
          <view class="day-list-body" wx:if="{{showIndex == index + 1}}">
            <view class="foodlist-box">
              <view class="day-body-foodlist">
                <image  src="../../images/caseDetails/red.png"></image>
                <view class="foodtask-desc">韩式甜辣能量棒 </view>
              </view>
            </view>
            <view class="day-list-body-footer">
              <view class="body-footer-title">
              可选加餐：
              </view>
            </view>
          </view>
      </view>
      <view class="programme-footer-text">
          <view class="footer-text-title">注意</view>
          <view class="footer-text-list">
              <view class="footer-text-list-sequence">1</view>
              <view class="footer-text-list-content">本方案所含代餐需要单独购买；</view>
          </view>
          <view class="footer-text-list">
              <view class="footer-text-list-sequence">2</view>
              <view class="footer-text-list-content"> 代餐中含有乳及乳制品，大豆制品、坚果仁制品和含有麸质的谷物及其制品，请自行核对过敏源；</view>
          </view>
          <view class="footer-text-list">
              <view class="footer-text-list-sequence">2</view>
              <view class="footer-text-list-content">  以下人群不建议使用此方案 </view>
              <view class="footer-content-list">   ·孕妇、哺乳期女性</view>
              <view class="footer-content-list">·正在使用降血压药的患者</view>
                <view class="footer-content-list"> ·糖尿病患者</view>
                 <view class="footer-content-list">·患有严重慢性疾病、贫血和重度低血糖人群 </view>
          </view>
      </view>
    </view>
  </view>
